{"tid":2501234,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法官：被告準備爆炸品以㒹覆香府及宣揚港獨，比葉繼歡更嚴重！","createTime":"2021-04-23T08:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T08:30:30.000Z","uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"88f6d7e4295c03d73b45db2716542ee99e61df34","tid":2501234,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:25:52.000Z","msg":"「香港民族陣線」成員盧溢燊前年在荃灣某工廈單位內，管有近1公斤的炸藥TATP（三過氧化三丙酮），早前承認1項管有爆炸品意圖藉以危害生命或財產罪。法官陳慶偉今午在高等法院指從其住處及手機搜證所得可見，被告準備及保存高爆炸性物品，以㒹覆香港政府及宣揚港獨，並屬主腦人物，屬最嚴重同類型案件，潛在危險比1997年葉繼歡案更大，刑責甚或比葉繼歡更重，判刑須極具阻嚇力，終判處被告監禁12年。"},{"pid":"9118388d48480a976b42cecca46aee8e8ca3a3d8","tid":2501234,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:26:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/2054580\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F2054580&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzi%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=37baca54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/2054580</a>"},{"pid":"c1c5475057c5679173c5d963a0187b29a9cc2bbc","tid":2501234,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1be2902b2c86b5b82a784e583303791868c5ca","tid":2501234,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:28:10.000Z","msg":"當日就咁係大廈引爆，如果係真爆炸品成KG有幾大殺傷力？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb18f7dfadcc8917ef9fc414b00750f873b0d161","tid":2501234,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb37f973c1d54903a79ecdeb1ddcb562ef7e19d9","tid":2501234,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6a1be2902b2c86b5b82a784e583303791868c5ca","tid":2501234,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:28:10.000Z","msg":"當日就咁係大廈引爆，如果係真爆炸品成KG有幾大殺傷力？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:29:39.000Z","msg":"應該係被人屈<br />\n手足做咁多嘢都係想移民姐<br />\n邊有可能咁癲做呢啲嘢<br />\n一被人發現點走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6d5c5848c0bfda48aadf3e8785cbc993587eb3","tid":2501234,"uid":241399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:30:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>楊光，GBM（1926年&mdash;2015年5月16號）係香港左派工會香港工會聯合會嘅前會長，喺1967年嘅<span class=\"red\">六七暴動組織同策劃一連串暗殺同放炸彈嘅暴動活動</span>，當中最出名係涉嫌指使殺害香港商業電台節目主持林彬，到香港回歸之後，喺2001年<span class=\"red\">獲香港特別行政區政府頒授大紫荊勳章</span>。</blockquote>"}]}